%F A029391 a(n) = floor((n^3+57*n^2+556*n+22500)/21600 - (n%2)*(n^2+33*n+453)/1440 + (((n+5) mod 6) - ((n+3) mod 6))*(n+9)/216 + ((n^2+3*n+2) mod 5)*n/50 - ((n^3+3*n^2+3*n) mod 5)/5). - _Hoang Xuan Thanh_, Jul 13 2026
